                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSpacerView",
                    "spacing": 16
                },

                {
					"class": "DepictionHeaderView",
					"title": "Known Issues"
				},                
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "- The battery can charge a bit over the defined target charge percentage, by 1% or 2%.\n- If the battery keeps charging over the target percentage at more than 5%, it means the tweak is not working correctly. Try a ***repring***, and if that does not work, try a ***userspace reboot***.\n- Wireless charging, or Apple charging cases. Currently I do not have a device or case to test those situations. If the battery does not stop charging at the target percentage, let me know."
                },

